00:37:50.640 --> 00:37:54.000
When there is light you discriminate and you start understanding

00:37:54.200 --> 00:37:59.160
that the truth is this and this is untruth.

00:37:59.400 --> 00:38:03.240
So when the Kundalini rises through your fontanel bone area

00:38:03.440 --> 00:38:06.160
the first blessing you get is of good health.

00:38:06.400 --> 00:38:09.120
That's the minimum that should happen, but is a by product.

00:38:09.320 --> 00:38:14.120
But I don't want to emphasize more on good health

00:38:14.320 --> 00:38:17.280
because tomorrow we'll get all the hospitals dropping on My head.

00:38:17.520 --> 00:38:20.680
That's what I don't want. You have to be first the Spirit.

00:38:20.880 --> 00:38:24.680
and you have to be the doctors and you yourself can treat

00:38:24.880 --> 00:38:26.760
your body as well as the body of others.

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:28.680
This is the minimum that should happen

00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:32.800
that you become a healthy person.

00:38:33.000 --> 00:38:36.000
Now what does that?

00:38:36.200 --> 00:38:40.840
Within us lies a power, which is evolutionary power,

00:38:41.040 --> 00:38:45.680
in the center, and it is the power

00:38:45.880 --> 00:38:48.480
which we call as

00:38:48.720 --> 00:38:54.440
the power of Mahalakshmi,

00:38:54.640 --> 00:39:00.160
is the power by which we sustain

00:39:00.400 --> 00:39:05.080
our own character, by which we become human beings.

00:39:05.280 --> 00:39:08.240
From Carbon where it is four valencies

00:39:08.480 --> 00:39:11.240
as human beings we develop ten valencies.

00:39:11.520 --> 00:39:14.880
We become

00:39:15.720 --> 00:39:19.760
eligible for our ascent through this power to begin with,

00:39:19.960 --> 00:39:23.080
because this is the power that gives us balance.

00:39:23.280 --> 00:39:27.040
In the gross it expresses itself as parasympathetic nervous system.

00:39:27.240 --> 00:39:29.360
Now what is parasympathetic nervous system?

00:39:29.560 --> 00:39:34.080
Is that it gives a balance to your sympathetic nervous system.

00:39:34.320 --> 00:39:37.080
Now sympathetic nervous system is the gross expression

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:39.800
of the two other powers which are around us

00:39:40.000 --> 00:39:44.680
one is the power of desire and another is the power of action.

00:39:44.880 --> 00:39:47.280
These sympathetic nervous systems

00:39:47.480 --> 00:39:50.120
come into play when we want to use them.

00:39:50.320 --> 00:39:52.520
For example if you want to run fast.

00:39:52.720 --> 00:39:56.920
So, when you are running fast these two powers come into power

00:39:57.160 --> 00:39:59.680
that they give us the force to run fast.

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:02.320
But what is the thing that brings it back to normal,

00:40:02.520 --> 00:40:04.960
is the central power that brings it to the normal

00:40:05.200 --> 00:40:08.040
or gives it a balance. So, this balancing force

00:40:08.240 --> 00:40:11.560
is the one that is responsible for your ascent.

00:40:11.800 --> 00:40:16.800
If you are not yet balanced, the same force will first balance you.

00:40:17.000 --> 00:40:20.000
