And the people who are too much right sided,

00:40:50.960 --> 00:40:52.160
who are too much speedy,

00:40:52.400 --> 00:40:54.680
who are thinking of the future all the time,

00:40:54.880 --> 00:40:57.120
they develop problems of the heart

