and go away because they get angry. But I'm for you,

00:44:25.120 --> 00:44:26.360
I'm, for your good I'm saying.

00:44:26.560 --> 00:44:29.160
Just understand that how can stress get out

00:44:29.360 --> 00:44:31.760
by this kind of a nonsensical thing happen to you.

00:44:31.960 --> 00:44:36.040
You are getting mad. This is not the way the stress has to get out.

00:44:36.240 --> 00:44:38.680
But you have to get over the stress.

00:44:38.880 --> 00:44:41.160
And that is a very simple thing to understand

00:44:41.360 --> 00:44:43.680
that if you are standing in the water,

00:44:43.880 --> 00:44:45.680
the waves are coming to you,

00:44:45.880 --> 00:44:48.080
coming and going, and you are afraid of the waves.

00:44:48.280 --> 00:44:49.880
But supposing by any chance,

00:44:50.080 --> 00:44:55.400
the state becomes that you become seated in a boat,

00:44:55.600 --> 00:44:57.360
somehow or the other, you rise up to that point

00:44:57.600 --> 00:45:00.680
that you are in a boat, then you enjoy the same waves from there

00:45:00.880 --> 00:45:02.680
and you don't mind any kind of thing.

00:45:02.880 --> 00:45:05.120
And this is the state one has to achieve.

00:45:05.360 --> 00:45:08.440
Unless and until you achieve that state, all your guru,

00:45:08.680 --> 00:45:11.760
all your money is of no value, nothing of the kind.

